service.name: Education Entry Payment
service.description: Education Entry Payment (EdEP) is payable to qualified recipients to aid in the costs associated in returning to full time study. Recipients of certain social security payments may qualify for EdEP if they are enrolled in an approved full time course of education or if a pensioner education supplement is payable.
